Suzlon Energy Plans to Acquire Remainder of German Unit REpower Systems

-- B y   H a r i   G o v i n d
-- 
2011-04-04T11:37:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-04/suzlon-energy-plans-to-acquire-remainder-of-german-unit-repower-systems.html
Suzlon Energy Ltd. (SUEL)  plans to acquire
rest of its German unit  REpower Systems AG (RPW)  to make it a wholly
owned subsidiary, it said in a statement to the National Stock
Exchange today.  The Indian company currently owns 95.16 percent in REpower,
according to the statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Hari Govind at 
 hgovind@bloomberg.net  